snippet.textDisplay: 5:22 - Line of scrimmage is at the 15 yard line. Wilson runs up to the 14 yard line before making his throw. The ball has clearly crossed the line of scrimmage and is therefore an illegal pass. For all the people complaining about that supposed "PI non-call" (which was correctly not called, Hollister initiated contact), the refs gave the Seahawks a TD that they shouldn't have gotten. How many more non-TDs do you want the refs to give them? On top of that, all scoring plays are reviewed and the refs didn't catch it.
